        {
          "type": "frame",
          "id": "3X5EG",
          "name": "notesCard",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "fill": "$surface-elevated",
          "cornerRadius": 18,
          "stroke": {
            "align": "inside",
            "thickness": 1,
            "fill": "$border-default"
          },
          "layout": "vertical",
          "gap": 14,
          "padding": 28,
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "iuid1",
              "name": "notesTitle",
              "fill": "$text-primary",
              "content": "System Notes",
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 24,
              "fontWeight": "700"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "KDZi1",
              "name": "notesDesc",
              "fill": "$text-secondary",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "A modal should interrupt only when interruption is the product intent.",
              "lineHeight": 1.5,
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 14,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "7zrj2",
              "name": "note1",
              "fill": "$text-secondary",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "1. Keep a single primary action. If two actions are equally important, the flow likely needs a different container.",
              "lineHeight": 1.5,
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 14,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "zo8rz",
              "name": "note2",
              "fill": "$text-secondary",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "2. The title should explain the decision. The body should explain the consequence. Avoid repeating the same sentence twice.",
              "lineHeight": 1.5,
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 14,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "uSKEJ",
              "name": "note3",
              "fill": "$text-secondary",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "3. Put secondary exit on the left or as the lower-emphasis option. Never style both actions as primary.",
              "lineHeight": 1.5,
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 14,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "NJMlb",
              "name": "note4",
              "fill": "$text-secondary",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "4. If the content needs side navigation, persistent context, or many sections, stop using a modal and promote it to a page.",
              "lineHeight": 1.5,
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 14,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
