              "fill": "$text-primary",
              "content": "System Notes",
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 24,
              "fontWeight": "700"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "d4sEV",
              "name": "notesDesc",
              "fill": "$text-secondary",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "Select should reduce ambiguity, not create a scavenger hunt.",
              "lineHeight": 1.5,
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 14,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "SkNbi",
              "name": "note1",
              "fill": "$text-secondary",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "1. Use select for known options. If users need to remember or type values, choose a different control.",
              "lineHeight": 1.5,
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 14,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "Wjac7",
              "name": "note2",
              "fill": "$text-secondary",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "2. Keep the trigger calm. Spend visual contrast on the open menu and the chosen option.",
              "lineHeight": 1.5,
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 14,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "8FWiu",
              "name": "note3",
              "fill": "$text-secondary",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "3. If the list is long, add search or regroup the information architecture instead of shrinking the option rows.",
              "lineHeight": 1.5,
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 14,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "Cl7SH",
              "name": "note4",
              "fill": "$text-secondary",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "4. Labels should stay visible in forms where the selected value alone might become ambiguous later.",
              "lineHeight": 1.5,
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 14,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
